The two explored a dark labyrinth.
In the depths, they found a lever...

A trap! They muscled their way out...
Thank goodness they had each other!

A trap! They artfully evade danger.
The labyrinth is theirs before long!

Trapped! ...And having fun with it!
They played to their heart's content.
